{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BB00623","text":"Aláahdi Diyin Nilíinii ts’ídá daats’í ’éí t’éiyá yá’át’éehgo hasht’e’ ninánihidoo’nilgo haz’á? Dooda, ‘éí doo ‘ákót’ée da.   Aláshdi Diyin Nilíinii t’óó nahdéé’ nihá yik’eh áhósingo dóó yee nihich’i yálti’íí bik’ehgóó ániit’éego ‘éí bee t’áá nihí ‘ádíká ‘anídiilwolgo haz’á. Bee ha’hóníinii dóó bee ‘adsiil nilíinii ts’ídá ‘éí t’éiya nihá hólóogo ‘ayósin Aláahdi Diyin Nilíinii. ‘Ayóó ‘ádayíníi’níigo bich’i’ ntsídeikeesígíí ‘éí Bá nideilnishii ‘ádaniit’é, áádóó ‘índa ts’ídá lá kót’éego ‘áda’joolíil dooleel ni niho’níigo yee nihich’i’ ntsékeesígíí t’aa nihil béédahózinígi ‘altso bik’ehgóó ádaniit’é, t’áá ‘altso bida’ííníilzin.\n\n* Is there any Remover of difficulties save God? Say: Praised be God! He is God! All are His servants, and all abide by His bidding!.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"1db6fa1d-1cae-47fe-b6b2-cd558265d999","book_cats":{"ar":{"cat":"الامتحانات والبلايا","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":7},"ar-translit":{"cat":"الامتحانات والبلايا","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":7},"az":{"cat":"Sinaq və çətinliklərdə oxunan dualar","cat_order":34,"order_in_cat":5},"be":{"cat":"Выпрабаванні і цяжкасці","cat_order":5,"order_in_cat":1},"bg":{"cat":"Помощ в изпитания","cat_order":22,"order_in_cat":3},"bn":{"cat":"পরীক্ষা ও  বিপদের সময়ের প্রার্থনা","cat_order":23,"order_in_cat":2},"bs":{"cat":"Pomoć u Nevolji","cat_order":22,"order_in_cat":3},"ca":{"cat":"Proves i Dificultats","cat_order":29,"order_in_cat":12},"ch":{"cat":"OTRO SIHA NA TINAITAI","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":6},"cnr":{"cat":"Teškoće","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":2},"co":{"cat":"Assistenza","order_in_cat":1},"cs":{"cat":"Pomoc a podpora","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":2},"cy":{"cat":"Assistance","order_in_cat":2},"da":{"cat":"Prøvelser Og Vanskeligheder","cat_order":31,"order_in_cat":7},"de":{"cat":"Prüfungen und Schwierigkeiten","cat_order":37,"order_in_cat":9},"el":{"cat":"∆ΟΚΙΜΑΣΙΩΝ ΚΑΙ ∆ΥΣΚΟΛΙΩΝ","cat_order":1,"order_in_cat":6},"en":{"cat":"Tests and Difficul